## Game Script Bucket Definitions

Score differential = `offense_score - defense_score` from the perspective of the
team whose features are being computed. Positive = leading, negative = trailing.

| Bucket | Score differential |
|---|---|
| Neutral | Within ±10 |
| Ahead | Leading 11–20 |
| Blowout lead | Leading 21+ |
| Behind | Trailing 11–20 |
| Blowout deficit | Trailing 21+ |

**Garbage time filter:** Leading 28+ in Q4 (period=4). Excluded from all buckets.
Not a feature bucket — a filter only.

